{"tid":639255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北韓大車禍】 32名中國遊客4北韓人死亡 翻車遇難","createTime":"2018-04-23T10:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T11:01:31.000Z","uid":82845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1eb2d3767025298f472538f8ccd5370a7c805d","tid":639255,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180423/large/1524458552_0f7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180423%2Flarge%2F1524458552_0f7c.jpg&h=3fdffed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180423/large/1524457545_e7d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180423%2Flarge%2F1524457545_e7d2.jpg&h=dc256c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一批中國遊客在北韓黃海北道遇上重交通意外，中國外交部證實，事故共造成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">32人死亡、2人重傷，情況極其危重，另有4名北韓人死亡</span></strong></span>，今日中午已經派出工作組及醫療專家前往北韓，前往協助。專門報道北韓消息的網站NK News早前的報道則指，<span style=\"color: red;\">這批遊客是北京一間旅遊公司的員工</span>，他們從瀋陽飛往北韓，事發時他們正從南部城市開城返回平壤途中，在惡劣天氣情況下，經過一段正在進行工程的道路時出事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180423/large/1524458679_c94b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180423%2Flarge%2F1524458679_c94b.jpg&h=7461b51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道引述北韓的消息指出，涉事的路段為配合北韓領導人金正恩，周五（27日）與南韓總統文在寅舉行峯會，北韓當局正在維修這個路段；事發時現場正在落着大雨，而且不時有狂風；消息又稱最少見到兩部救護車，晚上10時在平壤的街道上，消息稱這個情況「相當罕見」。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發出的聲明，只透露事故造成「重大人員傷亡」，沒有透露任何內容，網民都意識到事態相當嚴重，有網民稱：「重大事故，是指造成10人以上30人以下死亡，或者50人以上100人以下重傷，或者5000萬元以上1億元以下直接經濟損失的事故！」亦有曾經到北韓旅遊的網民稱，「朝鮮的路況車況都不好&hellip;親身感受&hellip;再說肯定不是在市區的馬路上出的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180423/58106874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58106874&d=8RN%2B%2FEQFj5W3xOX7Koq%2F4%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=f86fef21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180423%2F58106874&h=3a637bfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180423/58106874</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e09ce66ac174d632be1e5c3b1192385cbddbf18","tid":639255,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"北韓竟然冇封鎖消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc2cf2e174fcb4db752da5b162b31ab6cc8823","tid":639255,"uid":12947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"冇車都可以炒？"},{"pid":"9901b3beb6ab202aad610d4a606c8b0c0f05cf6e","tid":639255,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"北韓條路 車都唔多架, 都可以炒車, 個司機真係............<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d770ad668cafe18df88bacf8a93c8f1dcdacacc4","tid":639255,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccc2cf2e174fcb4db752da5b162b31ab6cc8823","tid":639255,"uid":12947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"冇車都可以炒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"爛地自炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2926e104e63d720d2854df9631a0f66a4cf71664","tid":639255,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:58:51.000Z","msg":"又真係永遠唔死多過37人架喎<im